434
00:33:06,434 --> 00:33:08,834
No joint motion for a continuance.

435
00:33:09,003 --> 00:33:12,029
No psychiatrist.
And trust me, pal, no plea bargain.

436
00:33:12,206 --> 00:33:13,867
Your boy's gonna suck the pipe.

437
00:33:14,442 --> 00:33:18,003
l don't know who you pissed off
to get this shit case and l don't care.

438
00:33:18,112 --> 00:33:19,079
No breaks.

439
00:33:29,257 --> 00:33:32,021
Mr. Young, DiMaggio is having
a great year.

