00:34:20,675 --> 00:34:21,869
Betty Grable.

453
00:34:22,009 --> 00:34:23,033
See?

454
00:34:25,680 --> 00:34:27,477
Says here she's just--

455
00:34:28,583 --> 00:34:29,743
How old are you?

