481
00:36:23,798 --> 00:36:27,256
l don't know yet. l haven't even spoken
to him about the case--

482
00:36:27,869 --> 00:36:29,427
One week, Counselor.

483
00:36:29,537 --> 00:36:32,973
Then you will either tell me
you are ready for the trial...

484
00:36:33,140 --> 00:36:37,099
...or you will come in here with a request
for a competency hearing.

485
00:36:37,311 --> 00:36:38,539
One week.

486
00:36:40,815 --> 00:36:42,783
This court is in recess.

487
00:36:58,666 --> 00:37:01,294
Mr. Young, you and me,
we've got to talk now.

488
00:37:02,003 --> 00:37:03,868
Would you like a cigarette?

489
