from the world-famous Fisherman's Wharf.</i>

730
00:49:36,523 --> 00:49:39,356
<i>We went to the streets
to find out public opinion.</i>

731
00:49:39,459 --> 00:49:42,485
You can't put a place on trial.
lt's a prison for prisoners.

732
00:49:42,596 --> 00:49:46,225
Now the murderers are accusing
the wardens of this and that.

733
00:49:46,333 --> 00:49:47,891
Doesn't make a lot of sense.

734
00:49:48,001 --> 00:49:50,094
Humson seems like a good guy.

735
00:49:50,203 --> 00:49:52,467
lf Alcatraz wasn't here l wouldn't live here.

736
00:49:52,539 --> 00:49:55,303
-You think it's too close?
-l think it's perfect.

737
00:49:55,475 --> 00:49:57,466
He's innocent until proven guilty.

738
00:49:57,577 --> 00:50:00,774
He'll get a fair trial, but, nonetheless,
he's a murderer.

739
00:50:01,048 --> 00:50:03,516
<i>This grizzly evidence bears mute witness...</i>

740
00:50:03,583 --> 00:50:06,746
<i>...to the brutal crime
